headline: Farmers Press Trump for Biofuels Boost to Counter Tariff Losses
summary: (Bloomberg) -- After losing their biggest export market due to Donald Trump’s trade wars, US farmers are now counting on the president’s support for biofuels to prevent their next crop from piling up in storage.
